snippet.title: Kero Quest 64 - Kickstarter and Demo Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Kero Quest 64 is a Collectathon 3D Platformer inspired by other games in the genre, especially those from the late 90s. You take control of Kero, a blue frog seeking to stop a prince from abusing his newly gained powers by collecting Magical Shards around the kingdom.

Please back us on Kickstarter at: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/837653174/kero-quest-64-froggy-retro-3d-platformer

Demo available now at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3411900/Kero_Quest_64
